This is a QGIS plugin to show a secondary coordinate system in the Statusbar (lower left).
For example, EPSG units or CalCOFI line/station

Tool tips explain all options. 

Install in QGIS:
  1. Plugins -> Manage and Install Plugins -> Settings,
  click the Add button for plugin repositories:
  
  2. Name: SecondaryCoordinates
     URL: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/edweber/SecondaryCoordinates/refs/heads/main/plugins.xml
    Ok
  
  3. Not Installed, Search or locate SecondaryCoordinates
     Install Plugin

You could also just download the SecondaryCoordinates.zip file from github and install in QGIS

